      "content": "that's a good start, really hits the atmosphere. can we get a bit more specific though? i need to describe the actual people you'd see hanging out on these corners or loitering near the buildings. like, what do they look like, what are they wearing, maybe some specific types of people that would make a protagonist feel like they're in the wrong part of town? just to really ground the grit in reality.",
